{"tid":1611422,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"做錯野都唔屌 我第一個就屌柒你地","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T20:13:09.000Z","uid":229387,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c2fc1360cff7002d29fef2429fab3b2bf24e73","tid":1611422,"uid":229387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"成班係咪發夢發到傻撚左？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔分化 唔割席</span></span><br />\n係當手足有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實質貢獻</span></span>先唔割<br />\n<br />\n一兩三次做得唔好，唔緊要 ，慢慢改。<br />\n點知四五六次都一樣係咁嘅撚樣？<br />\n比佢地形成一種覺得冇問題嘅習慣？<br />\n<br />\n就好似連基本嘅罷食罷買罷搭都唔做嘅人，<br />\n仲唔屌佢地一鍋？<br />\n勸又勸過，改又唔改，<br />\n屌完仲有機會直返呢<br />\n<br />\n隔黎有個post仲好笑 仲話唔好叫人偽勇武，<br />\n啲人玩跑Online開埋外掛啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跑完又唔上返前</span></span>"},{"pid":"47844e6e641fc52a34a474699a9b7e2b8f8806f3","tid":1611422,"uid":229387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36a6de201585860dc44a2718c1f49e1083fbf7ba","tid":1611422,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb13894f8e733f6bbae2eb24e3f231004b72f309","tid":1611422,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:13:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}